Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan u-turn on economy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wx80
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Jan 1983
President changes tack about economy and says government must take the lead in boosting growth. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less